* cgo - II

It is also possible to combine `Go` and `C` sources together inside a single package:

  $> mkdir $GOPATH/src/github.com/margo/my-cgo

Inside this new package, put 3 files: `main.go`, `my-cgo-lib.h`, `my-cgo-lib.c`.

